        ],
        "subject": {
          "reference": "urn:uuid:11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
        },
        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} has no significant past medical history. She has not been hospitalised previously and has no chronic conditions. She experienced two episodes of upper respiratory tract infection in the previous winter, both self-limiting. There is no history of recurrent tonsillitis requiring surgical intervention. {patientName} has a documented mild allergy to amoxicillin (urticaria). She does not take any regular medications. Her diet is balanced and age-appropriate; she is a non-smoker household (passive smoke exposure is nil as both parents are non-smokers). Immunisations are fully up to date per the Czech national immunisation programme. No recent travel abroad. Family lives in a standard urban apartment in Brno without known environmental hazards."
          }
        ]
      }
